===站房===
泾县站站房建筑面积4500平方米，以[[宣纸|宣纸]]卷轴为意向以凸显当地特色<ref>{{cite news|title=合福高铁泾县站旅游全攻略|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/155978421_745147|publisher=搜狐网|date=2017-07-10|accessdate=2017-10-10|archive-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828210124/http://www.sohu.com/a/155978421_745147|dead-url=no}}</ref>。候车室按每小时最高客流量1380人的标准设计<ref>{{cite news|title=合福高铁泾县站要建好啦|url=http://www.jxloufang.com/html/2015/jxnews_0117/2276.html|publisher=泾县新闻网|date=2015-01-17|access-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010055225/http://www.jxloufang.com/html/2015/jxnews_0117/2276.html|archive-date=2017-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
